<title>NSE - National Stock Exchange of India Ltd.</title>

With an objective of providing comprehensive and relevant company information to the retail investors, NSE and CRISIL have joined hands to publish company reports on companies listed on NSE. This unique and globally first initiative will aid retail investors' decision making process, by providing access to company reports and research at a central location from an independent and credible source.
The company reports will have the following information:
• Detailed financials for last 3 years including ratio analysis
These reports will also help in continuous flow of information to the investors; as the initial report would be followed up with three (3) quarterly updates with yearly and quarterly comparison.
The initiative has been sponsored by NSE-IPFT.
The reports are available for the following companies.
The Andhra Pradesh Paper Mills Limited
Commercial Engineers & Body Builders Co Limited
Dalmia Bharat Sugar and Industries Limited
Deepak Fertilizers and Petrochemicals Corporation Limited
The Great Eastern Shipping Company Limited
Gujarat Narmada Valley Fertilizer Company Limited
